{"tid":1999454,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"6.16延續義士遺志，爭取五大訴求周年遊行","createTime":"2020-05-03T07:46:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T17:00:40.000Z","uid":347812,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8a480dc0b5954eb37a974b718a4ba774256f4d56","tid":1999454,"uid":347812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T07:46:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【6.16延續義士遺志，爭取五大訴求周年遊行】</span></span><br />\n<br />\n學生動源於去年6月9日晚曾號召群眾留守金鐘至612，雖然最後當晚即場被警方驅散，但期後於反送中亦一直與群眾並肩作戰。<br />\n<br />\n過去數月街頭抗爭一直沉寂，義士一直未能沉冤得雪，因此我等已入紙申請「6.16延續義士遺志，爭取五大訴求周年遊行」，希望藉遊行重新號召全港市民再次走上街頭爭取民主自由，延續梁烈士等眾手足意志。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目的：延續義士遺志、重申爭取五大訴求<br />\n日期：6月16日<br />\n時間：2點半起步</span></span><br />\n<br />\n遊行路線：維園起步 - 高士威道 - 怡和街 - 軒尼詩道 - 金鐘道 - 添馬街 - 夏愨道 - 添美道政總外。<br />\n<br />\n*不反對通知書正在申請中<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/studentlocalism/2117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstudentlocalism%2F2117&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjggzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=1b30c96e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/studentlocalism/2117</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/329v2br.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F329v2br.jpg&h=8add743c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p7TMAws.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp7TMAws.jpg&h=201f8d80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JxP4nbt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJxP4nbt.jpg&h=17ae5642&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6839d36ff5679a805d8c3f2c967ef94c3ed9837b","tid":1999454,"uid":347812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T07:47:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hk